title: 50 Sci-Fi Classics Disk 10 of 10
description:
This is torrent 10 of 10 in this series.

I got this set a while back as bonus for placing a certain order through the Science Fiction Book Club. (http://www.sfbc.com)

Audio and video may leave something to be desired on some of these films, but keep in mind that these are classics, and you can enjoy them for what they are.

NTSC format.
